Newton.Henry N. Fisher House: The Henry N. Fisher House is a historic house at 120 Crescent Street in Waltham, Massachusetts. It is a ​2 1⁄2-story wood-frame structure, with the asymmetrical massing typical of Queen Anne houses. It has a wraparound porch with turned posts, lattice railing, and a sunburst motif in the gabled pediment above the steps.
